        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 2. (a–f) Hapalotremus spp. Habitus. (a, b) Hapalotremus carabaya sp. nov., female holotype. (c, d) Hapalotremus vilcanota sp. nov., female. (e) Hapalotremus vilcanota sp. nov., female and juvenile (white arrow) found under the same stone. (f) Hapalotremus vilcanota sp. nov. burrow. Photos: a, b, d–f: Tracie Seimon; c: Josh Richards." ;
